Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.56,0:00:14.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 快叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.44,0:00:18.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.15,0:00:20.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救護車就不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.36,0:00:23.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起那個快帶我去有暖氣的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.74,0:00:25.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,立刻馬上
