Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.19,Title - blur,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1193,880)\bord0\blur10\fad(695,695)}涼宮春日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.19,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(695,695)\pos(1193,880)}涼宮春日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.73,0:02:01.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說回來 你們是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.95,0:02:07.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.91,0:02:09.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對初次見面的人喘粗氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.78,0:02:11.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有點讓人害怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.33,0:02:14.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明是你說冷到瑟瑟發抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.29,0:02:16.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你當是誰把你背過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.92,0:02:17.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你面前的我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.08,0:02:21.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說過那種像是在雪山遇難的話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可是相當有魄力的說出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真討厭 不懂情趣的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.13,0:02:27.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.34,0:02:31.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很感謝你救了我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.51,0:02:33.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也真辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有這麼一個開不起玩笑的男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.73,0:02:38.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.90,0:02:41.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.27,0:02:45.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 我在說你啊 女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.20,0:02:49.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.41,0:02:52.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.12,0:02:57.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全不是那種關係…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.16,0:02:58.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不不…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.25,0:03:02.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是同一個社團的社員A和B
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.63,0:03:03.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.55,0:03:05.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是亳不相干的兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.72,0:03:09.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也完全不留情面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.39,0:03:11.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毫不相干啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.76,0:03:13.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這未免也太傷人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 就算這或許是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.10,0:03:20.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能至少把我當做朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.81,0:03:24.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 說成朋友就行了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說成朋友就行了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.03,0:03:33.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼害羞了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對於我來講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.66,0:03:39.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們沒在交往的話反而更容易相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把時間花在戀愛上的人 真是不知道在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.96,0:03:51.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,順便一提 我並沒有什麼痛苦的失戀經歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.51,0:03:53.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說中了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還真是被你們小看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引起這種無聊的誤會只會不愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.06,0:04:04.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁這個枧會 我要告訴你們我的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.27,0:04:07.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我對普通人類完全沒有興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.69,0:04:10.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更別提什麼戀愛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有興趣的是宇宙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉傳來的短信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.29,0:04:22.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛 長門快點回社團教室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.75,0:04:25.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕 在催我們收拾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.34,0:04:25.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.17,0:04:29.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就這樣吧 我也暖和了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們有事要辦的話就快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要去北高嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我們同條路呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼宮春日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道我名字的話不好搭話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.53,0:04:52.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且 被別人救了不做自我介紹也有點那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.07,0:04:54.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎 那我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.70,0:04:55.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.66,0:04:56.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫長門有希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有希啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說回來涼宮你為什麼那時候倒在地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.83,0:05:06.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因為我徹夜在公園待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.84,0:05:07.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了抓住聖誕老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.89,0:05:19.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,書包和錢包還忘在公園裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.39,0:05:23.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自然而然地讓你們請了客就沒注意到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.69,0:05:24.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自然而然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.27,0:05:28.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過 如果真是忘在公園的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.52,0:05:29.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要快點過去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.94,0:05:31.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 快點出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼 你們要特地陪我去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有錢包的話 連電車也坐不了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.28,0:05:42.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放著你不管就這樣回去的話 我們也不好受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟不上我可就丟下你們了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.63,0:05:50.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼我們要被丟下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.59,0:05:51.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快跟上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.44,0:06:08.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快看 沒事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那真是太好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這麼顯眼的地方也平安無事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這根本讓人不敢接近啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.33,0:06:26.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼宮 你真的想要抓住聖誕老人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.29,0:06:28.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才我不是都說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真厲害啊 從各種意義上來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.71,0:06:32.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你終於明白了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯 我很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.88,0:06:35.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}不 我不是在表揚你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.68,0:06:38.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.43,0:06:44.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 那個是給聖誕老人的訊息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真虧你知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.94,0:06:47.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在預先演習的時候我們見過面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.15,0:06:57.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂喂 你忘記了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 雖然我記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是因為是晚上臉看不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.20,0:07:05.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且從體格上來看還以為是男國中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還記得嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.71,0:07:15.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很清楚地記得哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.67,0:07:18.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我正是在等你自己注意到這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.47,0:07:24.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 我想要是我能夠再見你一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.14,0:07:27.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想跟你道個謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,道謝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.52,0:07:31.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我那時候非常的煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.94,0:07:35.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 是你推了我一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.69,0:07:39.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.24,0:07:40.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,STOP
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我完全沒有那種感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.78,0:07:48.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不記得做過值得讓你道謝的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.37,0:07:51.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且我都是為了我自己才接觸你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要是因此解決了什麼事 那是你的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那樣不就行了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.55,0:08:00.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,表揚一下自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.51,0:08:08.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你昨天說了同樣的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.60,0:08:09.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.73,0:08:10.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.14,0:08:14.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你能夠和我說一樣的話呢 刮目相看了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.81,0:08:15.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.90,0:08:16.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我微弱的感覺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是我的宿敵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.74,0:08:25.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真巧呢我剛剛也這樣感覺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼聖誕老人啊 笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊 存不存在都不先去驗證一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真虧你能說出那種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有必要去驗證吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那種事誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.13,0:08:40.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要可能性不為零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我都會繼續做下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟聖誕老人只是第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.85,0:08:51.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的目標是找出宇宙人 未來人 異世界人 超能力者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後在一起玩耍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.94,0:09:02.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人 雖然說了非常不著邊際的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知怎麼 卻非常的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的很厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.95,0:09:07.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.62,0:09:10.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是很厲害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是個厲害的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太慢了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.84,0:09:28.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 你迅速地把裝飾都收拾好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.47,0:09:29.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.60,0:09:32.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會盡快把這個杉樹處理掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 要忙起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.82,0:09:44.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聖誕節真讓人開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.58,0:09:51.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,意外的花了很多時間呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.87,0:09:56.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們要是不繞路直接過來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能更早做完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.92,0:09:59.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.17,0:10:01.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這孩子真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原諒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.64,0:10:12.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 下次再見面就是新學期了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不是該說祝你過個好年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 那再見了 祝你們過個好年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.15,0:10:26.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今年受你照顧了 祝你過個好年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才是 明年也請多關照了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼樣 長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？什麼怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.42,0:10:46.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好把你的心意傳達了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.43,0:10:51.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…我說了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.14,0:10:57.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,文藝社能夠繼續存在都是多虧了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.48,0:11:00.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來是那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.73,0:11:02.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是也不全是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要更加以自己為榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.99,0:11:08.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.91,0:11:11.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對我說同樣的話的人還有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.74,0:11:16.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎 今天早上和那個人又見面了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.87,0:11:17.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 味噌關東煮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.29,0:11:25.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的是個很厲害的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.09,0:11:30.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 味噌都滲進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還能見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.14,0:11:41.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是順便邀請阿虛一起新年參拜就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.56,0:11:42.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 好燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,決心還是遠遠不夠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.66,0:12:00.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今年一年 也請多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.42,0:12:02.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.01,0:12:13.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還真是用心 許了什麼願啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.43,0:12:16.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是問不得的問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新年快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.02,0:12:25.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新年快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽好了 今年也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.11,0:12:30.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今年也悠閒地度過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.65,0:12:31.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.83,0:12:42.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鎖定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.55,0:12:50.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.47,0:12:54.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有種海嘯要來的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.10,0:12:59.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喲 好久不見 我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 雖然到了北高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才想起來不知道你們到底在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.85,0:13:06.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就憑感覺找了找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,結果竟然有意外收穫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.19,0:13:12.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 這就是文藝社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.53,0:13:15.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍微有些冷清呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼來北高 是有什麼事情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.95,0:13:18.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就是隨便闖進來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然這麼堂堂正正的說出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.87,0:13:26.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 真虧你敢穿這樣在這亂晃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最大的問題就在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.13,0:13:30.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然大家都覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.09,0:13:34.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但都以為我是有事才過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.43,0:13:37.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只看外表的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.47,0:13:40.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說是光陽園的學生會長也說得過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「只看外表」這句讓我很在意耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.56,0:13:47.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 難得來了請 坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 謝謝 不過在那之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.07,0:13:51.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有個請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.28,0:13:55.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊 如果是很奇怪的事情我不會同意的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.28,0:13:58.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係吧 你只要借給我就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.70,0:14:00.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,運動外套和體操服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經可以進來了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.92,0:14:11.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了 這樣怎麼看都是在社團活動的學生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.51,0:14:14.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在才換上不會太晚嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的話確實是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.88,0:14:19.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還讓一個人在校門口等著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就穿這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一個人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這麼冷的冬天竟然讓人在外面等？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩個人的話不是太引人注目了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.77,0:14:32.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我就跟他說找你們兩位借衣服後就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.73,0:14:35.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能找到我們只是偶然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.28,0:14:37.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和計劃一樣很順利進行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.62,0:14:44.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不紮成馬尾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼 你喜歡馬尾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼特別的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也好 這樣更像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.73,0:15:05.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 你在幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古泉 快點換上這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.23,0:15:15.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊？在這裡換嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.53,0:15:20.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.74,0:15:23.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把頭髮留長好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.91,0:15:25.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.50,0:15:26.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.75,0:15:28.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.29,0:15:31.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為她的長髮很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在想我是不是也要學她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把頭髮留長一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.75,0:15:35.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.22,0:15:39.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實現在這樣不是挺好的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.38,0:15:44.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果長門想留長的話 也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在這樣其實就很適合你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,留長的話 請梳成馬尾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 好冷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都因為古泉磨磨蹭蹭的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.86,0:16:02.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在校門前換衣服果然還是會在意他人眼光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.08,0:16:08.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,初次見面 我是古泉一樹 請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.58,0:16:09.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.21,0:16:11.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼宮同學 我可以換回來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.42,0:16:14.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 不知道老師什麼時候會進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們兩個 大吃一驚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.92,0:16:21.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個古泉竟然就是謎之轉學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.68,0:16:23.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.80,0:16:26.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古泉是在去年入學典禮之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.56,0:16:29.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼一個微妙的時間點轉學過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.23,0:16:30.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很可疑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.89,0:16:33.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我為了讓他隨時可以露出真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.44,0:16:35.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才和他一同行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都已經過了半年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.32,0:16:39.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既不是謎也不是轉學生了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.82,0:16:42.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個真面目是指什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古泉的真面目？我想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}我能想到的就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}謎之組織的超能力間諜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}差不多那樣的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.63,0:16:46.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是叫古泉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.47,0:16:48.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 一般來說別人都會這樣覺得吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不這麼覺得嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.78,0:16:56.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}有希的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.95,0:16:59.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}是啊…最後真實身份是外星人如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}對不起 我是地球人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.06,0:17:00.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人 在我們學校也被認為是異端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.81,0:17:01.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.36,0:17:03.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.73,0:17:08.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在微妙的時期轉學過來而被孤立的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.11,0:17:09.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.28,0:17:12.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 我說你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.12,0:17:18.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她單純把我當作一個普通的轉學生而接受我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.88,0:17:27.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過 涼宮同學也就對我是轉學生這屬性感興趣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.05,0:17:30.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過最近好像開始厭倦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也有點著急了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.39,0:17:35.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也沒必要著急吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.60,0:17:38.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 因為…嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喜歡涼宮同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.23,0:17:44.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你腦袋沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.56,0:17:46.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不覺得她很有魅力嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.82,0:17:49.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我認真聽啊 這是很重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.07,0:17:54.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.24,0:17:59.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從現在開始 我跟古泉隸屬於北高文藝社的神秘部門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.16,0:18:03.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我同時還是文藝社真·社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣可以吧 社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.67,0:18:07.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.46,0:18:11.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還真隨便啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.02,0:18:20.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.39,0:18:24.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,北高 fight 0n fight 0n
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.56,0:18:27.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就是涼宮同學啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.61,0:18:28.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.65,0:18:33.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道讓外面的學生進社團教室這事被發現了會多麻煩嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎？嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 社長都這麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.67,0:18:48.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的可以啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一開始還以為是被威脅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過看到長門同學的眼睛後 我就懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再說要是知道是在做壞事 會盡力隱瞞的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.26,0:19:03.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再加上名門光陽園的學生應該不會做出冒失的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.85,0:19:05.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不不 朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不僅僅是冒失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.40,0:19:07.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這傢伙 還相當白癡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.40,0:19:09.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請多指教×2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.95,0:19:20.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.25,0:19:25.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帶好東西來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.33,0:19:29.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.21,0:19:32.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又來啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.96,0:19:36.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,社團教室的佔領行動順利的進行著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鏘~美如畫的美少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼我會被拐到這裡來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.48,0:19:48.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼嘛 朝比奈學姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呿 你們認識啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.94,0:19:54.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這學校可是個名人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.95,0:19:59.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然能突破鶴屋學姐的防禦把她帶到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那威脅已經被兩個寶貴的犧牲品擋住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.58,0:20:06.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,犧牲品？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.46,0:20:11.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來跟兩個男生還沒回來有關係呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.59,0:20:14.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是你們也跟來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.46,0:20:17.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就不會發生那種戰鬥啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.76,0:20:20.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以才把阿虛借給你了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.39,0:20:25.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙完全沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.51,0:20:58.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.34,0:20:59.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.51,0:21:03.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 在這種地方跳起來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會被看到內褲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.31,0:21:06.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要懲罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.64,0:21:12.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個叫阿虛的是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.98,0:21:15.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對我的態度一天比一天差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.15,0:21:19.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特別是對待有希和對我的態度差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.90,0:21:21.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是那樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是這社團的真·社長阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.66,0:21:25.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他也只是個平民社員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.54,0:21:27.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.29,0:21:31.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,意外的 那種對待相處起來會更容易 不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.71,0:21:37.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,確實 不用敬語會更好說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.25,0:21:40.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,基本上 別人看我都覺得我是個怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}鶴屋？現在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.69,0:21:45.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}文藝社喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.66,0:21:43.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至現在為止他們都一直用敬語來跟我說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.96,0:21:45.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別一臉冷靜的說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.54,0:21:49.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來在這裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.05,0:21:52.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次一定要拿回我的實玖瑠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.55,0:21:57.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想奪回去就用蠻力來搶呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.31,0:22:05.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.06,0:22:07.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.48,0:22:09.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.32,0:22:11.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.69,0:22:14.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇 我想要那青蛙頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.40,0:22:16.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你給我等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.99,0:22:19.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然想偷看美少女的內褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.12,0:22:21.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還早了兩億五千六百年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.32,0:22:24.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}不 我沒看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.12,0:22:27.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾經寧靜的文藝社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.84,0:22:34.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然熱鬧起來了
